						<div class="postbody">I made a little prototype of the window method (with leading) using Python and pygame: <!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="http://thefox.aspekt.fi/platformer-camera.py">http://thefox.aspekt.fi/platformer-camera.py</a><!-- m --> (Set DRAW_WINDOW to True to see the window/trap.)
